snippet.title: Champion Unmasked: Hawkgirl
snippet.description:
This is one mace that you don't want to take to the face. Hawkgirl is soaring into Infinite Crisis on January 21st, and you can learn more about this high-flying warrior in today's Champion Unmasked!

Want to take to the skies and defend the DC Comics Multiverse? Play Infinite Crisis for free at http://www.infinitecrisis.com!
